name: Great Zhanzhu Lantern: "Pathblocker Maximus"
description: A big, exquisite lantern modeled after the red Jade-Cradling Zhanzhu, a character many children absolutely detest after hearing the story of "Zhanzhu the Moon-Devourer."\nShrink not when the Pathblocker Maximus stands in your way, for it can sense the fear in every person who approaches...
